{"tid":673431,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高職期中考試題問校長是誰？　校方：基本觀念","createTime":"2018-05-21T23:39:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-22T03:14:12.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1da398151216c5317353b778da7153a2e1417f26","tid":673431,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T23:39:09.000Z","msg":"有家長向《蘋果》投訴說，孩子就讀彰化高商，但期中考試國防課的考題最後兩題選擇題的題目，竟然是問校長是誰?主任教官是誰?直說這種考題跟啟智班的有何不同?可說是造神運動，認為校方相關人員不適任，要求教育部官員應嚴懲。對此校方表示，是基本觀念的教育，外界認為不妥，將會檢討改進。<br />\n<br />\n該校校長說，該考試是高三學生在三月底的期中考試，經詢問命題教官認為，一個學生在校內應該知道師長是誰，進入職場後也應該知道相關的直屬長官是誰，不要只是知道直屬長官，卻連公司負責人是誰卻不知道。<br />\n<br />\n命題教官還認為，這是基本的做人做事態度，希望藉此提醒學生，不要輕忽。雖然考題簡單，但態度很重要。(詹智淵／彰化報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180522/640_193a603054e800f872cff2eee03881fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180522%2F640_193a603054e800f872cff2eee03881fd.jpg&h=1813063c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180522/1357977/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180522%2F1357977%2F&d=Cf9YCzyxC9ID9a6tD1u72S7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=2dac09c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180522%2F1357977%2F&h=b93e4b69\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180522/1357977/</a>"},{"pid":"c96ffb1e89c8b682d7273ae056db05a63409864b","tid":673431,"uid":7125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T00:34:45.000Z","msg":"屌搵位送分姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35b7c3d410631a8e79dbe449e16bba014b7bc4ed","tid":673431,"uid":78304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T03:02:32.000Z","msg":"我只認錢， sor9ry"},{"pid":"3e310b05c15fbee3e6b56bb